## Relationship Between the Two Sheets

These two sheets operate as a connected system:

| Staff Time Entry | Direction | Monthly Support Tracker |
|---|---|---|
| Staff log time in **Time Entry** tab | → | Informs hours-used in **Master Tracker 2026** |
| **Live Monthly Client Totals** accumulates monthly hours per client | feeds → | Master Tracker balance columns via Lookup Key |
| **Helper** tab holds plan/tier/maintenance metadata | mirrors → | **Client Directory** plan/tier fields |
| **Monthly Summary** shows total hours by client | informs → | Which clients are at or over their monthly allocation |

**The Monthly Workflow:**
1. Staff log entries in Staff Time Entry → Time Entry tab throughout the month
2. At month end, Live Monthly Client Totals is finalized per client
3. Master Tracker 2026 is updated: hours-used pulled via Lookup Key, monthly hours refreshed for managed plans, balances carried forward
4. Client-facing monthly summary docs are generated from the Master Tracker

