## Key System Notes

**Lookup Key** (`YYYY-MM|domain`) is the join key between the two sheets. It must be consistent in both to work correctly.

**Plan Tier codes** follow a pattern:
- `RadiateU-0`, `RadiateU-3`, `RadiateU-5` — RadiateU-branded managed plans
- `Starter-0`, `Starter-1` — Starter tier
- `Grow-0`, `Grow-1` — Growth tier
- `Pro-1` — Pro tier
- `Premium-2` — Premium tier
- `Managed Plus` — Top managed tier
- `Hosting` — Hosting-only, no support
- `Other-Block-0`, `Other-1` — Other/block arrangements

**Maintenance schedule indicators (Staff Note emoji) are standardized:**
- ✅ Monthly maintenance — included in plan, proceed
- ⛔ Hosting only — approval required before work
- 🚫 No maintenance — bill before work
- ❓ Semi-annual — check last service date; additional work billed as support
- ⚠️ Bill maintenance as support (not included in plan)

**Partner agencies** (Mode Effect, Professional Punch, Stimuli Media, Made Better Studio, Positive Element, Right Stuff Media, Stimuli Media) are tracked with their own contact info but follow normal billing rules with the partner as primary contact.

**~60+ client domains** are tracked in the system. Only clients with Track Time Entry = Yes in the Client Directory flow into active billing logic.
